Encapsulation
- it acts as protective layer which put restriction to access the data by access modifier
- it can be achieved through protected and protected
- it provides security by hiding the data from the outside world.

Abstraction is the property by virtue of which only the essential details are displayed to the user, implementation pasrt is hidden

